name: Cyprus
description:
This image is a painterly render from a photo. Also a collab piece with @d_centrlaysh on Twitter.
This is her hometown where she grew up. She doesn't live there anymore and i wanted to give her a piece of home to have. So i'm going to ship her when i can afford it a physical canvas of this to have in her home. We all grow up and we all end up missing our childhood, our hometown. Well this is my gift to you. Thanks for letting me collaborate with you on this piece.
